      <title>Android热更新技术总结</title>
      <link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2017/10/26/android%E7%83%AD%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/</link>
